tags.description: This site was an industrial area, is mostly paved with some gravel. Some areas are grassy due to non-maintenance. The area is a de facto park - maintained by the city parks service - there are plans in place for development.
tags.name: Saint Helens Waterfront Park
tags.note: This area is part of a larger waterfront development project. More information at the URL in the 'website' metadata.
